                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>, <date>March\n                                                  7th. 5612</date>.</p>\n                              <p>Dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I did not receive a letter from my brother in\n                                        answer<lb/> to the one I wrote him during your visit here\n                                        until a<lb/> few days back and therefore did not write\n                                        before but<lb/> now according to promise I do.</p>\n                              <p>My brother says he shall reply to you but having been<lb/> very\n                                        much engaged in the affairs of Sussex Hall<lb/> he has not\n                                        until now had time to write to you,<lb/> or me, he says\n                                        having interested himself for<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Dr. Benish's</persName> Bible, (the Pentateuch of\n                                        which is published,<lb/> and having obtained more\n                                        subscribers than will cover<lb/> the cost of it, he is now\n                                        going on with the other part<lb/> of the Bible,) he is sorry\n                                        he cannot dispose of your<lb/> Bibles, but with regard to\n                                        the Occident he will<lb/> with pleasure try and do all he\n                                        can, but he says,<lb/> the English do not like subscribing\n                                        to foreign<lb/> periodicals although written in their own\n                                        language,<lb/> I suppose he will write you more fully on\n                                        the<lb/> different subjects you wrote him about as he does\n                                        not<lb/> mention much about them to me therefore I can\n                                        conclude<lb/> that subject.</p>\n                              <p>No doubt you would be interested in a little of the<lb/> English\n                                        news, The Great Synagogue Dukes<add>?</add> place has\n                                        voted<lb/> 6000 pounds sterling towards building a Synagogue\n                                        at<lb/> the <placeName>west end</placeName>. A Public\n                                        Meeting of the Jews was<lb/> called by <persName>Dr.\n                                                  Adler</persName> at Sussex Hall for the</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rj49f4b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
